DISTRIBUTION.—The species has been reported from Argentina , Brazil , and Venezuela (Sanborn 2013; Sanborn & Heath 2014 ; Barreto & Porfiro 2015 ;
Dias et al . 2017
;
Maccagnan et al. 2018
) with recent additions of records for Colombia , Ecuador (without locality) ( Barreto & Porfiro 2015 ), Bolivia , Paraguay ( Sanborn 2019b ), and Peru ( Sanborn 2020b ).
